# Stray sample media / documents. Do NOT commit data files to the repo root —
# keep prose under docs/ and bundled assets inside the package. Root-level media
# globs catch future strays; the named entries below are the ones removed from
# tracking. (CLAUDE.md / README.md / *.md docs are intentionally NOT ignored.)
